      <title>俄罗斯精炼燃料出货量因柴油流量减少而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/russia-s-refined-fuel-shipments-edge-down-as-diesel-flows-shrink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于柴油出口减少，俄罗斯石油产品出口在 11 月份因更多炼油厂结束季节性维护而出现反弹，上周出口略有下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/russia-s-refined-fuel-shipments-edge-down-as-diesel-flows-shrink</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 10:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
