      <title>国际能源署维持悲观看法，但制裁谈判导致油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在俄罗斯和伊朗威胁加大对石油出口限制后，油价连续第四天上涨，但国际能源署 (IEA) 再次发出供应过剩警告，导致油价维持在窄幅区间内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 23:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
